---
title: get_base_fee_per_blob_gas (EIP-7918)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init
    q_init --> q_read_excess : excess = parent.excess_blob_gas
    q_read_excess --> q_read_fraction : fraction = blobSchedule.baseFeeUpdateFraction
    q_read_fraction --> q_compute : blob_base_fee = fake_exponential(MIN_BASE_FEE, excess, fraction)
    q_compute --> q_final : return blob_base_fee
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_compute
        INV-006: blob_base_fee >= MIN_BASE_FEE (1 wei)
        INV-007: Uses new blobSchedule.baseFeeUpdateFraction after fork
    end note
